Well, in my option DI is one of the worst parts of Angular. It&#x27;s a module system which can&#x27;t be integrated with anything. Doing something like commonjs/amd would be much nicer:<p>app.controller(&#x27;Name&#x27;, function(require) {
    var $scope = require(&#x27;$scope&#x27;);
    var y = require(&#x27;some-service&#x27;);
});<p>And suddenly, no problems and no weird syntax!
